<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Email</title>
    <style>
      td { padding: 20px 30px; } .main-conatiner { margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto; width: 470px; max-width: 470px; padding: 1.25rem;
      border-collapse: collapse; text-align: center; } .para-text { font-style:
      normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 12px; line-height: 130%; color:
      #404040; text-align: justify; } .banner { font-style: normal; font-weight:
      400; font-size: 10px; line-height: 13px; color: #616161; background:
      #f5f8f9; border-left: 2px solid #1c9cf6; padding: 4px 10px; } .table-data
      { font-family: "Tahoma"; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size:
      10px; line-height: 132.5%; color: #262626; } .table-row { padding: 10px
      10px; } .table-row-top { padding: 10px 5px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body
    style="
      padding: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      font-family: Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif;
    "
  >
    <div class="main-conatiner" width="470px">
      <table style="margin: auto; text-align: center">
        <tbody>
          <tr style="padding-bottom: 60px">
            <td>
              <img
                src="../../public/media/images/nbol-email-logo.png"
                alt="company logo"
                {{! height="78px"
                width="200px" }}
                style="height: 60px; width: 180px"
              />
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="para-text">
              <p style="border-left: 2px solid #ffcd00; padding-left: 10px">
                Dear
                {{firstName}}
                {{lastName}},
              </p>
              <p style="padding-left: 10px">
                As part of the recently launched survey - [Survey Name], you
                have been selected to provide feedback for the following
                employees -
              </p>
              <p style="padding-left: 10px">
                Your role in this feedback is to provide feedback on leadership
                competencies of the person(s) you are rating. The survey results
                will provide valuable information for the person(s) leadership
                development and will not be used for any other purpose.
              </p>
              <p style="padding-left: 10px">
                Your answers are completely confidential and will be summarized
                with the data from other raters in the same category. The
                results of all surveys will be compiled by NBO group, per
                request of [Tenant Name], so no one else will have access to
                your individual feedback.
              </p>
              <p style="padding-left: 10px">
                Please click on the link(s) in the below table to start
                completing the surveys.
              </p>
              <p style="padding-left: 10px">
                You need to complete the survey(s) no later than [End Date].
                Your timely completion of the survey is highly appreciated.
              </p>
              <p style="padding-left: 10px">
                If you have any questions, please contact [Correspondence Name]
                at [Correspondence Contact No] or email [Correspondence Email].
              </p>
              <p style="padding-left: 10px">
                Yours Sincerely
                <br />
                NBO Leadership
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="padding-top: 44px;">
            <td style="text-align: start">
              <p
                style="
                  font-style: normal;
                  font-weight: 400;
                  font-size: 12px;
                  line-height: 14px;
                  color: #0069ff;
                  padding-bottom: 5px;
                  border-bottom: 1px solid #3786ee;
                  font-family: 'Trebuchet MS';
                "
              >
                SURVEY PARTICIPATION STATUS
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <table
        width="410px"
        style="width: 410px; max-width: 410px; margin: auto;"
      >
        <tbody>
          <tr style="text-align: start">
            <td class="table-data table-row" style="background: #f5f9ff">
              Feedback for
            </td>
            <td class="table-data table-row" style="background: #f5f9ff">
              Relationship with Ratee
            </td>
            <td class="table-data table-row" style="background: #f5f9ff">
              Link
            </td>
            <td class="table-data table-row" style="background: #f5f9ff">
              Status
            </td>
          </tr>

        </tbody>
      </table>

      <table
        width="410px"
        style="width: 410px; max-width: 410px; margin: auto;padding-top: 20px ;"
      >
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <p
                style="padding-top: 10px; border-top: 1px solid #F2BF1A; font-style: normal;
              font-weight: 500;
              font-size: 12px;
              line-height: 10px;
              font-family:'Trebuchet MS';
              text-align: center;
              "
              >&copy; NBO Leadership</p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding-top: 0px;">
              <img src="{{facebook_logo}}" alt="" style="padding-right: 8px;" />
              <img src="{{twitter_logo}}" alt="" style="padding-right: 8px;" />
              <img
                src="{{instagram_logo}}"
                alt=""
                style="padding-right: 8px;"
              />
              <img src="{{linkedin_logo}}" alt="" style="padding-right: 8px;" />
              <img src="{{youtube_logo}}" alt="" />
            </td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>